'AMPERGONE' ALLOWS YOU TO REMOVE ANAPPLESOFT ARRAY FROM MEMORY UNDERPRODOS. TO INSTALL THE UTILITY; JUST'BRUN AMPERGONE'. WHEN YOU WANT TOINVOKE IT; USE A STATEMENT THATASSIGNS ANY VALUE TO AN ELEMENT OFTHE TARGET ARRAY. FOLLOW THEASSIGNMENTIMMEDIATELY WITH AN '& name'STATEMENT; WHERE name IS THE NAME OFTHE ARRAY TO DESTROY.FOR EXAMPLE; THE FOLLOWING LINEREMOVES THE ARRAYS A$ AND B FROMMEMORY: A$(0) = "": & A$: B(0) = 0: & B